data.title: Adp 2021-22
data.meta_description: ADP 2021-22 - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document contains a list of projects in the Annual Development Plan (ADP) for 2021-22. It includes 17 projects under the Prime Minister's Office with allocations totaling over Tk. 10,872 crore. It also lists 7 projects under the Cabinet Division with allocations of over Tk. 2,757 crore. Furthermore, it outlines 4 projects under the Public Administration Ministry with total allocations of over Tk. 15,785 crore.
